      "cookedHtml": "<p>Tired of switching between tools to log time? Struggling to keep track of billable hours or team productivity? We built <strong>TimeBits</strong>—a seamless <strong>time-tracking app for <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a></strong>—to solve these exact problems!</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228252-what-is-timebits-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228252-what-is-timebits-1\"></a><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/magnifying_glass_tilted_left.png?v=15\" title=\":magnifying_glass_tilted_left:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":magnifying_glass_tilted_left:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> What is TimeBits?</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>TimeBits</strong> is a powerful yet simple time-tracking app designed <strong>natively for <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a></strong>. It lets you log, manage, and analyze time spent on tasks—without ever leaving your workflow.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/e/d/ed2c9eec52f79dda93939c0de2352f616a1044e0.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/e/d/ed2c9eec52f79dda93939c0de2352f616a1044e0_2_690x355.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"355\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1919×988 150 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228252-why-did-we-build-it-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228252-why-did-we-build-it-2\"></a><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/light_bulb.png?v=15\" title=\":light_bulb:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":light_bulb:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Why Did We Build It?</strong></h3>\n<p>As a <strong>certified <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> partner</strong>, we noticed teams wasting time on:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Manual timesheets</strong> (spreadsheets, sticky notes, or juggling multiple apps).</li>\n<li><strong>Guessing billable hours</strong> instead of tracking real work.</li>\n<li><strong>No visibility</strong> into where time was actually going.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>So we created <strong>TimeBits</strong>—to <strong>simplify time tracking, improve accountability, and make data-driven decisions easy</strong>.</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228252-what-does-timebits-do-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228252-what-does-timebits-do-3\"></a><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/high_voltage.png?v=15\" title=\":high_voltage:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":high_voltage:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> What Does TimeBits Do?</strong></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Log Projects &amp; Tasks</strong> – Our Monday app lets you add trackable projects &amp; tasks.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Detailed timesheets</strong> – See daily, weekly, or project-based time logs.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Billable hours &amp; reporting</strong> – Export data for payroll, invoicing, or productivity insights.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Team visibility</strong> – Track time across projects without micromanaging.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/d/1/d1eb76228440734905bbcc48652c8bdc142543b6.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/d/1/d1eb76228440734905bbcc48652c8bdc142543b6_2_690x353.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"353\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1918×984 179 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228252-real-world-use-cases-4\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228252-real-world-use-cases-4\"></a><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/hammer_and_wrench.png?v=15\" title=\":hammer_and_wrench:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":hammer_and_wrench:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Real-World Use Cases</strong></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/one.png?v=15\" title=\":one:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":one:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Freelancers &amp; Agencies</strong> – Track billable hours per client/project.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/two.png?v=15\" title=\":two:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":two:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Remote Teams</strong> – Monitor productivity without invasive screenshots.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/three.png?v=15\" title=\":three:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":three:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Dev &amp; Creative Teams</strong> – Measure time spent on sprints, edits, or design tasks.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/four.png?v=15\" title=\":four:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":four:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Consultants</strong> – Auto-generate timesheets for client invoicing.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/4/3/43c3397903ac0e6993b478dd03d469925d03979e.jpeg\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/4/3/43c3397903ac0e6993b478dd03d469925d03979e_2_690x355.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"355\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1918×988 180 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228252-who-are-we-5\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228252-who-are-we-5\"></a><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/waving_hand.png?v=15\" title=\":waving_hand:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":waving_hand:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Who Are We?</strong></h3>\n<p>We’re <strong>Creative Bits</strong>, a <strong>certified <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> partner</strong>, and we build apps to supercharge your workflow. TimeBits was born from our own frustration—now we’re sharing it with you!</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228252-how-to-use-timebits-6\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228252-how-to-use-timebits-6\"></a><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=15\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> How to Use TimeBits</strong></h3>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Install</strong> from the <a href=\"https://timebits.creativebits.app/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com Marketplace</a>.</li>\n<li><strong>Add the TimeBits column</strong> to any board.</li>\n<li><strong>Start tracking time</strong>—it syncs instantly!</li>\n</ol>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228252-any-dependencies-7\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228252-any-dependencies-7\"></a><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/link.png?v=15\" title=\":link:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":link:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Any Dependencies?</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Works on <strong>all <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> plans</strong> (no enterprise required).</li>\n<li>No extra tools needed—runs <strong>100% inside <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a></strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228252-pricing-8\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228252-pricing-8\"></a><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/money_bag.png?v=15\" title=\":money_bag:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":money_bag:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Pricing?</strong></h3>\n<p>Our plans start from a simple plan of $15 per month for up to 5 users to unlimited users for $2000 only<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Free plan</strong> 14-days free trial<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Premium plans</strong> for advanced reporting &amp; team features.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/b/2b3ce50a8b81f036078e7e9ebac8608fb0d98b34.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/2/b/2b3ce50a8b81f036078e7e9ebac8608fb0d98b34_2_635x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"635\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1090×858 41.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228252-stop-wasting-time-tracking-time-9\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228252-stop-wasting-time-tracking-time-9\"></a><strong><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/hourglass_not_done.png?v=15\" title=\":hourglass_not_done:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":hourglass_not_done:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Stop Wasting Time Tracking Time!</strong></h3>\n<p>Try <strong>TimeBits</strong> today and turn hours into actionable insights.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Get it here:</strong> <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000550/timebits\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">TimeBits - monday.com Marketplace</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/speech_balloon.png?v=15\" title=\":speech_balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":speech_balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Questions?</strong> <a href=\"https://creativebits.us/contact-us/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Drop them here— We’re happy to help.</a></p>\n<p><span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#MondayDotCom</span> <a class=\"hashtag-cooked\" href=\"/tag/timetracking\"><span class=\"hashtag-icon-placeholder\"></span><span>timetracking</span></a> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#Productivity</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#RemoteWork</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#FreelancerTools</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#WorkOS</span></p>"
